00:33:32.400 --> 00:33:37.080
more, because I, I think there are a lot of 
interesting things and we are really eager

00:33:37.080 --> 00:33:44.340
to hear also from WordPress developers, and 
designers, and users, and I hope that, that

00:33:44.340 --> 00:33:49.620
you will all be interested in this project 
and also reach out to us to to learn more.

00:33:53.340 --> 00:34:02.160
[Roberto] Awesome. Um, well, we can give it a couple of minutes 
and see if there is another question on YouTube.

00:34:12.720 --> 00:34:19.440
Okay, we have a question. Uh, the 
testers need to be multilingual?

00:34:21.840 --> 00:34:26.940
Good question, thank you. Uh, no. The 
