00:37:07.020 --> 00:37:14.820
Well, personally, I think that, that we are hiring 
people with disabilities in our company. I think

00:37:14.820 --> 00:37:18.780
that is the biggest achievement for to me 
personally, I believe the key to inclusion

00:37:18.780 --> 00:37:25.200
is to have a workplace, um, and really that we have 
been able to not only hire people ourselves, but

00:37:25.200 --> 00:37:30.600
also help other young people with disabilities 
to get into the workforce. That is what I'm most

00:37:30.600 --> 00:37:35.820
proud of in my professional life. That is not 
really accessibility, as such, but I think that is

00:37:35.820 --> 00:37:45.300
my sort of spontaneous answer to that question. 
[Roberto] Awesome, thank you very much as I think Lnn

00:37:45.300 --> 00:37:52.320
also ask, for the previous question, if the time 
that you describe is also include the training?

00:37:55.020 --> 00:38:02.940
[Susanna] Well, there's no training, really here. In the, I mean 
the testing is just really simple prototypes, so

00:38:02.940 --> 00:38:09.180
you are doing the same thing as you're normally 
doing as when you're creating content. You are

00:38:09.180 --> 00:38:13.920
writing a text, you are adding a link, you're 
adding an image, and then you are supposed to

00:38:13.920 --> 00:38:18.540
add the alt text, and so on. So you are performing 
this, this sort of the user scenario from the,

00:38:19.080 --> 00:38:25.440
from the web authoring perspective. And then 
there's really a short instruction on what we

00:38:25.440 --> 00:38:30.060
want you to do to perform that test. So it's not 
really, I wouldn't say it's training, uh, really.

00:38:30.060 --> 00:38:36.000
So it's a short instruction, then you perform 
the text, test and then that is screen recorded,

00:38:36.000 --> 00:38:40.920
so we can see what you do. So that is sort of 
fine, but we also always ask you if you have

00:38:40.920 --> 00:38:45.180
any comments or suggestions or anything. We're 
really happy if you want to share with us your

00:38:45.180 --> 00:38:49.440
thoughts, so you also have the possibility 
to answer some questions afterwards, if you,

00:38:49.440 --> 00:38:55.020
if you would like to. But it wouldn't take more 
than 15 minutes just to do one, one of the items.

